This thing was made with Tinkercad. Edit it online <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.tinkercad.com/things/1x0WK8tb4Kr" >https://www.tinkercad.com/things/1x0WK8tb4Kr</a>
I designed this to fill the deadbolt hole in an exterior door being used indoors in our makerspace. 
This will work in a 1.75&quot; thick door, it does not screw together fully. When fully screwed together the gap between the two gears is 1.33&quot;
